f1fab3e54fba6c0e80749d627f","tid":145292,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/ivyl4gwn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fivyl4gwn&h=26ba9da2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n 個廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今次呢個廣告撚唔屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你哋係咪弱智架on9賤畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講極都唔化　講極都唔明　屌你老母<br />\n都話Google有技術令廣告非常匹配內文內容<br />\n有相關性幾乎係必然、係賣點　如果唔係佢啲廣告收入唔會咁掂<br />\n你哋班弱智仔係咪覺得「嘩，又會咁啱得咁橋嘅？真係好好笑啊」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n鬼唔撚知 拎岀嚟笑下得唔得呀屌你老母 <br />\n係咪覺得自己屌鳩啲廣告撚好大義凜然好撚醒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n總係有啲人以為自已好撚醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16b247fa3fc9ec19773ca591bc8f23df5bdd448","tid":145292,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/05/224342_1819675e4c6ed1f499d45471466286c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F05%2F224342_1819675e4c6ed1f499d45471466286c1.jpg&h=9d028233&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0341e174838d653f0454a6cb7239a8b18c8520d","tid":145292,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:37:08.000Z","msg":"jm,我bf刀系靠賭為生，雖然系有公，但佢情緒好反覆，佢輸錢我會好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2969ea57fa1df60de9a72dd20544d819749d3ba","tid":145292,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:12:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">生髮療程全撚部都係呃鳩人錢架</span></span> <br />\n一係食藥，一係植髮，一係織髪 <br />\n無架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a279e4a1cc20b0a3be5b9684314804bf5b7482c","tid":145292,"uid":37329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:19:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22a04e48e1b36baf3c6da7b451bccbb7531f164f","tid":145292,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:21:22.000Z","msg":"認真，搵民主黨<br />\n佢前排做過幾單，係女士喺美容院<br />\n高壓式巨額簽course嘅case"},{"pid":"5fe0e1a310d724443ee80acb04942270aab37761","tid":145292,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:31:56.000Z","msg":"又copy babykingdom D 文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602017a70e4bb2595c47cd758a452b35af2cc88c","tid":145292,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同老公結婚幾年，住係奶奶到，因為大家決定要買樓，應承左要努力草錢<br />\n之前諗住開聯名戶口，但我夾唔到時間都簽名所以一直都拖住左無開<br />\n我信晒佢，出左糧就俾我個份錢佢草，草左幾年，草到而家至少有50幾萬<br />\n我一直都無乜過問佢d野，覺得佢唔會呃我<br />\n新年執屋，拆信見到佢月結單，見到戶口得返30萬左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我即時問佢係咪轉左d錢去其他戶口<br />\n佢睇到張單，唔出聲<br />\n我發晒癲咁嘈，問佢d錢去左邊，佢見我喊先肯出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話用左20幾萬去買生髮療程，佢話唔想禿頭禿到變地中海....<br />\n我聽到又嬲又傷心，無諗過佢一直呃我，拎我地d錢去做自己野咁自私<br />\n最嬲係佢拎返所謂「生髮療程」嘅野比我睇，完全就係呃人嘅垃圾<br />\n佢蠢到比20幾萬人地！！！<br />\n我d fd叫我離婚...話呢個男人信唔過...自私...唔可靠<br />\n佢係咁同我道歉，話佢以後會草多d錢填補返...我都唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後 我d fd介紹左史雲遜活<span style=\"color: red;\">鬆</span>中心比我老公<br />\n話佢地服務好好 價值又公道 又有好多成功例子<br />\n最後我老公真係試左試 佢去完都讚好<br />\n人又自信左 頭髮又多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲因為咁工作順利左 最近仲升埋職<br />\n我諗個20萬對我地以後黎講都係小數目</blockquote><br />\n字都打錯點做打手"},{"pid":"e2cb213875c1bbd928ab856b38d8245eebdc35f3","tid":145292,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUfgVDV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUfgVDV.jpg&h=03b35c46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/201446_cfc4817ae29b039a2bed67d263769b4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F201446_cfc4817ae29b039a2bed67d263769b4a.jpg&h=d5e3c41e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2250e82d612fb359e1fb442e1ccdb0ded51df5","tid":145292,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUfgVDV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUfgVDV.jpg&h=03b35c46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/201446_cfc4817ae29b039a2bed67d263769b4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F201446_cfc4817ae29b039a2bed67d263769b4a.jpg&h=d5e3c41e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n( Show Blocked User - 祖赫特 )"},{"pid":"a55f0847d1403e5c979ea7a5d3ba091010294b03","tid":145292,"uid":74315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:25:07.000Z","msg":"廿萬好閒<br />\n但有個咁on9既老公離婚算啦"},{"pid":"497474025ba391cb0a459566c4d279be365a3fdf","tid":145292,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:37:09.000Z","msg":"草你老母"}]}